<span id="freeTextContainer3880259814884990303">Because I&apos;m not in the habit of reading book blurbs before I start a novel, I was half way through this book before I realized it&apos;s fiction based on true historical figures, in this case artist Camille Pissaro and his mother. Since I was already loving the beautiful language and setting of St. Thomas, the historical context only added depth.<br/><br/>Another real winner from Alice Hoffman, whose work I love.</span>
  <span id="freeText3880259814884990303" style="display:none">Because I'm not in the habit of reading book blurbs before I start a novel, I was half way through this book before I realized it's fiction based on true historical figures, in this case artist Camille Pissaro and his mother. Since I was already loving the beautiful language and setting of St. Thomas, the historical context only added depth.<br /><br />Another real winner from Alice Hoffman, whose work I love.</span>
